00:20:36.097 --> 00:20:37.898
I don't regret
what happened with Haochen.

00:20:39.418 --> 00:20:40.498
But I know it has

00:20:40.537 --> 00:20:41.777
caused you and Mom

00:20:41.777 --> 00:20:42.698
tremendous stress.

