This is my fault.

00:20:46.218 --> 00:20:47.938
I had a bad temper before.

00:20:48.498 --> 00:20:49.617
I acted tough

00:20:51.258 --> 00:20:52.857
because I was insecure

00:20:53.418 --> 00:20:54.097
and anxious.

00:20:54.738 --> 00:20:56.698
